在2012年，長春龍被歸類於新建立的[[熱河龍科|熱河龍科]]，這個[[演化支|演化支]]還包含[[何耶龍|何耶龍]]、[[長春龍|長春龍]]，可能還有[[韓國龍|韓國龍]]、[[越龍|越龍]]<ref name=Han>{{cite journal |last=Han |first=Feng-Lu |coauthors=Paul M. Barrett, Richard J. Butler, and Xing Xu |year=2012 |title=Postcranial anatomy of Jeholosaurus shangyuanensis (Dinosauria, Ornithischia) from the Lower Cretaceous Yixian Formation of China. |url=http://www.tandfonline.com/doi/full/10.1080/02724634.2012.694385 |journal=Journal of Vertebrate Paleontology |volume=32 |issue=6 |pages=1370-1395 |doi=10.1080/02724634.2012.694385 |access-date=2013-01-06 |archive-date=2019-07-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190710181141/https://www.tandfonline.com/doi/full/10.1080/02724634.2012.694385 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

